October was amazing 💕
I went home to Milwaukee and spent time with family. I had the opportunity to speak to students at UWM. I went to Chicago and had brunch.  I spent a week in Puerto Rico with family. I Rode a horse for the first time I ate gooood and partieddd. I went back to my new home Vegas and visited a national park. I went to my favorite med spa I took my self for sushi more times than im willing to admit. I dressed up for Halloween and had so much fun with people that have been so welcoming to me. Long story short October was beautiful 🥹
Keep playing slow w y’all cheap ash 😂

Shoot day 📸
My favorite day is shoot day! 🥰I’ve been shooting with this hair company for 3years now. Landing me on hair packages and beauty supply store fronts across the US.

Ok ok! I’m super emotional right now because this year has been nothing short of AMAZING. Not only did I move across the country ALONE. But I continue to THRIVE despite the growing pains. 🥹
I’m at the point in my life that I’ve done everything I said I would do as a girl from Milwaukee and my inner child is so PROUD. I guess it’s time to dream again. I can’t wait to see what 2024 brings. 💭

Thank you everyone!
